131Ch 26:1 The divisions of the gatekeepers£º From the Korahites£º Meshelemiah son of Kore, one of the sons of Asaph.
131Ch 26:2 Meshelemiah had sons£º Zechariah the firstborn, Jediael the second, Zebadiah the third, Jathniel the fourth,
131Ch 26:3 Elam the fifth, Jehohanan the sixth and Eliehoenai the seventh.
131Ch 26:4 Obed-Edom also had sons£º Shemaiah the firstborn, Jehozabad the second, Joah the third, Sacar the fourth, Nethanel the fifth,
131Ch 26:5 Ammiel the sixth, Issachar the seventh and Peullethai the eighth. (For God had blessed Obed-Edom.)
131Ch 26:6 His son Shemaiah also had sons, who were leaders in their father's family because they were very capable men.
131Ch 26:7 The sons of Shemaiah£º Othni, Rephael, Obed and Elzabad; his relatives Elihu and Semakiah were also able men.
131Ch 26:8 All these were descendants of Obed-Edom; they and their sons and their relatives were capable men with the strength to do the work--descendants of Obed-Edom, 62 in all.
